channel.title: InsidiaX client problems
channel.description: I recently downloaded the client and source and it works perfectly with the source. However, my current source is ErasedPkz, and I wanted to use the InsidiaX client with the ErasedPkz source. But when I do that, everything works great...except the hits. Whenever I attack a NPC or player , the hits don't show up at all. Anyone know how to fix this? Would appreciate it.
